pullRequest.bodyText:
While testing i saw the following (silly) errors:

Send Workspace Collaborators Status as ACTIVE to RDR

commit.message: Correct few things for RDR Flow

nodes.bodyText: Side note: this kind of issue would have been easily caught by a unit test. Be sure to follow-up soon on developing unit tests, which was a condition of approval for #2948. (It might help to track a separate Jira ticket for tests follow-up, so we can include it in sprint pointing). I would recommend including this service as being in scope for unit test coverage.
